hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I saw your advert in the paper gabapentin in neuropathic pain syndromes a randomised double-blind placebo-controlled trial Six more guides were highly commended. Bhupendra Sharma, who guides in India and Nepal with G Adventure, Carlos Vivar (Guatemala with Viaventure), Carl Meadows (North Korea with Regent Holidays), Cathy Harlow (Iceland with Discover the World), Don McFadzien (Antarctica with Aurora Expeditions), and Neil Williams (Central America with Tucan Travel).
